Changes: + new, - removed, * cleanup, @ bugfix:

@ fix poll()
@ Remove bad get_ctrl()'s
* Reduce ioctl stack usage
* Remove final ";" from some macro definitions
* Better support for SN9C103
+ Add sn9c102_write_regs()
